reviewText: I watched 3 times  I really loved it.
Cute movie.  My 13-year-old daughter loved all of them!
My kids went to see Legally Blonde as as musical so got this for them to see the movies and they really enjoyed the "Blondies" movie which was a bonus
Great clean movies. My daughters enjoy them.
I bought the trilogy and thought all three movies were great.  Tons of laughs and suitable for the entire family. A nice way to spend the evening.
Legally blonde one and two are classics and hilarious but I was not so impressed by the third movie. It does not have the same humor.
love the 3 movies together in one case the product was dellivered on time and the price was good I was very pleased with this purchase

I ended up only receiving the first Legally Blonde; the other two DVD's wouldn't play, but nevermind.  I have watched this movie countless times and enjoy it every time.  I have two grown daughters and can relate to the primping and crimping of the sorority girls.  We have also had several Chihuahuas!  I never tire of watching this....
